Onboard The Faithful

“Are you sure little lady, the ship has many fine and valuable things? You’re choosing to free these two? “Yes, Yes, these two were on the shalapoon that sank, they are my father’s servants.” -“Please can I choose them?” – ” The captain said you have the first choice, so if that’s your choice that’s fine by us.”
